{"tid":2199742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國大選] 拜登對中政策接近川普，WSJ：美中關係換總統仍將激烈摩擦","createTime":"2020-09-12T12:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T14:35:01.000Z","uid":52658,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0953cb86e96afaef91f6e75d8be402283c9b45c4","tid":2199742,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T12:20:26.000Z","msg":"美國總統大選逼近，如何應對中國是雙方互批的廝殺焦點之一。《華爾街日報》分析，即使明年一月白宮易主，華府對中國的強硬路線仍不會改變，美中之間仍將摩擦激烈。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨籍前總統歐巴馬（Barack Obama）任內的亞太事務助理國務卿坎貝爾（Kurt Campbell），目前是拜登競選團隊的高級顧問。他表示，民主黨內已普遍體認到，川普對中國掠奪性行為的判斷，大致是準確的。<br />\n<br />\n拜登也曾抨擊川普應對中國的策略不當，表示他會更密切與美國盟友合作，展開全球性的向北京施壓倡議。他認為，川普若與盟國合作抗中會更有效，而非在對抗中國的同時，又與歐洲、加拿大、墨西哥、南韓、日本等盟友展開貿易對抗。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，拜登陣營的幕僚中，許多都曾任職於歐巴馬政府。不少人回首過去，認為當時對中政策太軟，太慢體認到習近平有獨裁者的傾向。<br />\n<br />\n歐巴馬總統任內，原本希望與中國建立更密切的關係，曾要求時任副總統的拜登與習近平建立交情。拜登曾誇耀自己與習近平相處的時間，比任何外國官員都多，包括兩人一起吃飯的時間總計25小時，一同旅行的長度累計2.4萬哩（約3.8萬公里）。<br />\n<br />\n曾任共和黨籍前總統小布希（George W.Bush）時期的國務院官員、現任外交關係協會（Council on Foreign Relation）主席哈斯（Richard Haass）就說，無論誰當選總統，美國未來5年的對中政策都會比過去5年更強硬，「中國變了，美國對中國的看法也變了」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200911/YMX26M5REBB6TLMFDRQSGEYGAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200911%2FYMX26M5REBB6TLMFDRQSGEYGAE%2F&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=8879dbe5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200911%2FYMX26M5REBB6TLMFDRQSGEYGAE%2F&h=af3cd030\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200911/YMX26M5REBB6TLMFDRQSGEYGAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n是日搖擺州民調<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYWpXuH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYWpXuH.png&h=a1181717&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LfckvPH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLfckvPH.png&h=b23d1dec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vbM5GWo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvbM5GWo.png&h=c04ef811&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5EKyQPK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5EKyQPK.png&h=3319b994&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9638e3971741ae6d885f113d3c6d2ad6111241e3","tid":2199742,"uid":34869,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T12:21:16.000Z","msg":"邊撚度接近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daeed9acc32eee6b4d1ab30bcefc84daaeca4167","tid":2199742,"uid":370061,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T12:22:36.000Z","msg":"係係係！實信你架！所以拜登贏梗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80f2be91f8422e8251522af9581cec03a122ba6","tid":2199742,"uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T12:23:47.000Z","msg":"拜登呃完選票就話之你啦。選總統係保佢自己同家屋人唔使被調查咋。"},{"pid":"af1c212c83acea59edbc09589500758fd142dbf5","tid":2199742,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T12:26:12.000Z","msg":"拜燈係度扮乜春"},{"pid":"6f0ca42069b006df9734d621b833aca6992bfbcf","tid":2199742,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T12:28:14.000Z","msg":"好難信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff20ad8ede846cbb167dd944c129d202ed7e9230","tid":2199742,"uid":17008,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T12:30:15.000Z","msg":"拜登曾誇耀自己與習近平相處的時間，比任何外國官員都多，包括兩人一起吃飯的時間總計25小時，一同旅行的長度累計2.4萬哩（約3.8萬公里）。<br />\n<br />\n太熟係優點定缺點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8489168f2da6251fc1fa2a08b8f6b0926805c3be","tid":2199742,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply